Example Data

Source: R/old-data.R
old_data.Rd

An example tibble of example 'old' data.

Usage

old_data

Format

An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 3 rows and 9 columns.

Details

lgl

A logical vector.

int

An integer vector.

dbl

A double vector.

chr

A character vector.

fct

A factor.

ord

An ordered factor.

dte

A Date vector.

dtt

A POSIXct vector.

hms

A hms vector.

Examples

old_data
#> # A tibble: 3 × 9
#>   lgl     int   dbl chr      fct     ord   dte        dtt                 hms   
#>   <lgl> <int> <dbl> <chr>    <fct>   <ord> <date>     <dttm>              <time>
#> 1 TRUE      1   1   most     most    most  1970-01-02 1969-12-31 16:00:01 00'01"
#> 2 FALSE     4   4.5 most     most    most  1970-01-05 1969-12-31 16:00:04 00'04"
#> 3 NA        6   8.2 a rarity a rari… a ra… 1970-01-07 1969-12-31 16:00:06 00'06"
